org.bukkit.event.player

  • org.bukkit.event.playerを使用しているパッケージ 
    パッケージ 説明
    org.bukkit.entity
    Interfaces for non-voxel objects that can exist in a world, including all players, monsters, projectiles, etc.
    org.bukkit.event.player
    Events relating to players.
